title: Eric Slick on The Big Lebowski
itunes:title: Eric Slick on The Big Lebowski
description:
Eric Slick is the drummer for one of Chuck's favorite bands, Philadelphia's native sons, Dr. Dog. Eric and Chuck had an awesome talk about band life, drumming, touring, and Eric's favorite all-time movie, The Big Lebowski. The dude abides, y'all.
